'''霍普·希克斯'''<ref name=guancha>{{cite web |author1=徐乾昂 |title=贴身助手确诊，特朗普立刻接受检测，开始隔离 |url=https://www.guancha.cn/internation/2020_10_02_566997.shtml |website=[[观察者网|观察者网]] |accessdate=2020-10-02 |date=2020-10-02}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Hope Hicks}}，{{bd|1988年|10月21日}}）是美国[[公共关系|公共关系]]专员、[[唐纳德·特朗普|特朗普]]政府高级政治顾问。<ref name=NYT13Feb2020>{{Cite news|last=Haberman|first=Maggie|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/13/us/politics/hope-hicks-white-house-return.html|title=Hope Hicks to Return to the White House After a Nearly Two-Year Absence|date=February 13, 2020|work=The New York Times|access-date=February 13, 2020|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213153602/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/13/us/politics/hope-hicks-white-house-return.html|archive-date=February 13, 2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>希克斯2017年1月至9月间曾担任{{tsl|en|White House Director of Strategic Communications|白宫战略交流主管}}，2017年8月至2018年3月间任{{tsl|en|White House Communications Director|白宫通讯联络主管}}。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/09/12/us/politics/trump-hope-hicks-white-house-communications-director.html |title=Hope Hicks Is Formally Named White House Communications Director |last=Haberman |first=Maggie |date=September 12, 2017 |work=The New York Times|access-date=September 14, 2017 |issn=0362-4331 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914081914/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/09/12/us/politics/trump-hope-hicks-white-house-communications-director.html |archivedate=September 14, 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/trump-bids-farewell-close-aide-hope-hicks/story?id=54098040|title=Trump bids farewell to close aide Hope Hicks|first=Jordyn|last=Phelps|date=March 29, 2018|website=ABC News|accessdate=April 5, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180404185535/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/trump-bids-farewell-close-aide-hope-hicks/story?id=54098040|archive-date=April 4, 2018|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年3月29日她一度从特朗普政府请辞，后又于2020年3月9日官复原职。2021年1月13日，希克斯二度辞职。<ref>{{cite web |last1=CNN |first1=Pamela Brown and Jamie Gangel |title=Top White House adviser Hicks no longer works at the White House, a previously planned departure |url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/13/politics/hope-hicks-white-house-trump-riot/index.html |website=CNN |accessdate=2021-01-14}}</ref>

希克斯曾经当过模特，供职在[[特朗普集團|特朗普集團]]旗下，后在[[2016年唐納·川普競選美國總統|2016年特朗普参选]]期间担任{{tsl|en|press secretary|新闻发言人}}、早期通讯联络主管。{{tsl|en|Presidential transition of Donald Trump|唐纳德·特朗普总统交接|总统交接}}期间，希克斯担任特朗普政府的新闻发言人。<ref name="marie">{{cite web |url=http://www.marieclaire.com/politics/news/a20905/donald-trump-communications-director-hope-hicks/ |title=Meet Donald Trump's 27-Year-Old Communications Director, Hope Hicks |last1=Nelson |first1=Rebecca |website=Marie Clare |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128014010/http://www.marieclaire.com/politics/news/a20905/donald-trump-communications-director-hope-hicks/ |archivedate=January 28, 2017 |dead-url=no |accessdate=January 22, 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.politico.com/blogs/donald-trump-administration/2016/12/donald-trump-hunting-conservation-trip-232863 |title=Trump transition seeks distance from conservation fundraiser |last1=Nussbaum |first1=Matthew |accessdate=December 21, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221005520/http://www.politico.com/blogs/donald-trump-administration/2016/12/donald-trump-hunting-conservation-trip-232863 |archivedate=December 21, 2016 |dead-url=no |work=Politico }}</ref>她在2018年辞职时是特朗普麾下任职时间最长的政治助理。<ref name="tot">{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/26/style/hope-hicks-donald-trump.html |title=The Woman Who 'Totally Understands' Donald Trump |last1=Grynbaum |first1=Michael |date=June 26, 2016 |website=The New York Times |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106190116/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/26/style/hope-hicks-donald-trump.html |archivedate=January 6, 2017 |dead-url=no |accessdate=January 21, 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.townandcountrymag.com/society/politics/news/a9056/hope-hicks-facts/ |title=15 Things You Should Know About Hope Hicks, Donald Trump's Director of Strategic Communications |last1=Dangremond |first1=Sam |website=Town & Country |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230161932/http://www.townandcountrymag.com/society/politics/news/a9056/hope-hicks-facts/ |archivedate=December 30, 2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>离职期间，希克斯担任[[福斯公司|福斯公司]]的公关负责人兼常务副总裁。<ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/10/08/media/hope-hicks-joins-fox/index.html|title=Former Trump aide Hope Hicks joins Fox as head of PR|last=Selter|first=Brian|publisher=CNN|date=October 8, 2018|accessdate=October 26, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181026232749/https://www.cnn.com/2018/10/08/media/hope-hicks-joins-fox/index.html|archive-date=October 26, 2018|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{cite web|url=https://www.foxcorporation.com/management/executive-team/hope-hicks/|title=Hope Hicks Executive Vice President and Chief Communications Officer|accessdate=May 30, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530171434/https://www.foxcorporation.com/management/executive-team/hope-hicks/|archive-date=May 30, 2019|dead-url=no}}</ref>

